  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a clay pot over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the shrimp and chicken breast and cook until browned.",
    "add the cooked rice, diced tomato, smoked paprika, and salt to the pot.",
    "stir in the peanuts and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15 minutes.",
    "let the paella rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
